{"tid":210893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋賣到500萬　顯徑邨成歷來最貴公屋","createTime":"2017-04-21T09:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T20:34:16.000Z","uid":31208,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d948e424bf4e4799a4755d97fdb49065f5965ebd","tid":210893,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"4月21日(五) 16:53<br />\n公屋賣到500萬　顯徑邨成歷來最貴公屋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓市已步入前所未見「癲市」，香港開埠以來，出現首間500萬元公屋。資料顯示，沙田公屋顯徑邨顯富樓高層6室，實用面積544方呎，以500萬元成交，實用呎價9,191元。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上址成交金額創全港公屋新高，對上青衣公屋長安邨2016年底售443萬元，為對上公屋成交價最高紀錄。"},{"pid":"96384615bf1a54850dc2d784a80cfcd8ea3c3581","tid":210893,"uid":107765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"想上車？我諗我淨係上到巴士"},{"pid":"22cd907aae76d37749ddbf27501978db2c95b5ad","tid":210893,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"果度唔係大圍咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7c032cbf90aa958ee1d351db81fd58bb202b9c","tid":210893,"uid":78089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"講地理個位係幾好既..遲下對面仲有大大個顯徑站出九龍港島..但5球幾野我不如買返大圍站附近啲屋苑私樓唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c8929d64931f7bb5004e36fc91033be8b14c38","tid":210893,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"老揀實 肯定做出黎啦 500萬唔新樓都圓買居屋啦 走去買公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45cded301d0c777870a0e9801a37cff838bf341","tid":210893,"uid":84381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁多人鐘意住公屋<img src=\"/